" KEYMAPPINGS

" escape shortcuts
imap jj <esc>
imap ii <esc>

" navigate split screen panes
nnoremap <C-Left> <C-W>h
nnoremap <C-Down> <C-W>j
nnoremap <C-Up> <C-W>k
nnoremap <C-Right> <C-W>l

" open a terminal
"nmap <C-j> :terminal<CR>
" when in terminal mode close
"tnoremap <C-j> <C-\><C-n>

" comment/Uncomment the current line
map <C-c> :Commentary<CR>


